  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\"><img alt=\"Stone Crows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/50px-Stone_Crows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/75px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/100px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Gurn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\"><img alt=\"Stone Crows.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/50px-Stone_Crows.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/75px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Stone_Crows.svg/100px-Stone_Crows.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Vale_mountain_clans\" title=\"Vale mountain clans\">Vale mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor\" title=\"Gunthor\">Gunthor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gurn</b> is the father of <a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor\" title=\"Gunthor\">Gunthor</a>, a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Crows\" title=\"Stone Crows\">Stone Crows</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Mountains of the Moon\">Mountains of the Moon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if Gurn is still alive.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gurn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404093341\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.057 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.236 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 418/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10378/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5116/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 315/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip 